    "body": "Hey @MoMannn, this is possible although not documented by Waffle:\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\npragma solidity ^0.8.0;\r\n\r\ncontract Foo {\r\n  event Event();\r\n\r\n  constructor() {\r\n    emit Event();\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst { expect } = require(\"chai\");\r\nconst { ethers } = require(\"hardhat\");\r\n\r\nit(\"Should emit an event in the constructor\", async function () {\r\n  const Foo = await ethers.getContractFactory(\"Foo\");\r\n  const foo = await Foo.deploy();\r\n  await foo.deployed();\r\n\r\n  await expect(foo.deployTransaction).to.emit(foo, \"Event\");\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\nPlease use [our Discord server](https://hardhat.org/discord) if you have more questions!",
